-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| DATASTAX STUDIO                                                           |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Starting DataStax Studio

    1. Run the shell script to start Studio.

         $ cd /usr/local/bin/datastax-studio-6.8.21
         $ ./bin/server.sh


    2. To run Studio, navigate to:

         http://127.0.0.1:9091


    3. To stop Studio:

         $ pkill -f studio



- Instructions 

    (https://community.datastax.com/articles/12265/how-to-connect-to-astra-db-from-datastax-studio.html)

    1. Create an application token

    2. Create a secure application bundle

    3. Add a new connection with these creds in DataStax Studio